---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Conventions"
  description="Details for the Bastrop County Republican Party's County Convention and the Republican Party of Texas State Convention."
>
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-20 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-8 text-center tracking-tight">2026 Republican Conventions</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-navy max-w-none bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-red-primary text-center uppercase tracking-wide">Attention Bastrop County Republican voters.</p>
        <p class="text-center italic text-text-secondary -mt-4">(Please see official notice of County Convention below)</p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-0">County Convention</h2>
        <p>BCRP will hold the Bastrop County Republican Party's County Convention at the following location:</p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-navy my-6 font-medium text-lg shadow-sm">
          <p class="m-0"><strong>Family Worship Center</strong><br />
          2425 FM 1704<br />
          Elgin, TX 78621</p>
        </div>

        <p>The Bastrop County Republican Party's "County Convention" will be held on <strong>March 28th, 2026 beginning at 9:00am.</strong></p>

        <p>To be eligible to participate in the County Convention you must have been nominated and elected as a Delegate or Alternate at your Precinct Convention. Guests are welcomed to attend, but must be recognized by the Convention Chair to speak.</p>

        <p>The agenda and committee meetings will take place following the opening ceremony. State Convention Delegates and Alternates will be nominated and elected. Issues approved at the Precinct Conventions will be discussed and if approved will be sent forward to the State Convention.</p>

        <div class="my-12">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-4 text-center">Official Notice of County Convention</h3>
          <img src="/convention-notice.png" alt="Official Notice of County/Senatorial Convention" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-300 mx-auto" />
        </div>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">State Convention</h2>
        <p>The Republican Party of Texas' "State Convention" will be held at the George R. Brown Convention Center in Houston. Committee meetings will begin <strong>June 8th, 2026</strong>, with the Convention beginning <strong>June 11th thru June 13th 2026</strong>.</p>
        
        <p>To be eligible to participate in the State Convention you must have been nominated and elected at your County Convention as a Delegate or Alternate.</p>

        <div class="bg-navy/5 p-6 rounded-xl mt-8">
          <p class="m-0 font-medium text-navy text-center">Please contact your <a href="/about/precinct-chairs/" class="text-red-primary hover:underline">Precinct Chair</a> or <a href="/about/county-chair/" class="text-red-primary hover:underline">County Chair</a> for additional details for these two conventions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
